sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Agent
  participant PromptOps as PromptOps API
  participant LLM as LLM Provider
  participant AIEval as AI Eval (separate)

  Note over Agent: 1. Discovery — find or register the asset

  Agent->>PromptOps: GET /assets/shadow.daily-report
  alt asset exists
    PromptOps-->>Agent: 200 Asset
  else 404
    Agent->>PromptOps: POST /assets {id, owner, contracts}
    PromptOps-->>Agent: 201 Asset created
    Agent->>PromptOps: POST /assets/{id}/versions {body, snapshots}
    PromptOps-->>Agent: 201 Version (draft)
    Agent->>PromptOps: POST /assets/{id}/versions/{vid}/promote
    PromptOps-->>Agent: 200 Version (active)
  end

  Note over Agent: 2. Retrieve active version (most common)

  Agent->>PromptOps: GET /assets/{id}/active
  PromptOps-->>Agent: 200 Version body + contract snapshot

  Note over Agent: 3. Render with runtime inputs

  Agent->>PromptOps: POST /versions/{vid}/render {inputs, save:true}
  PromptOps-->>Agent: 202 rendered_system, rendered_user, rendered_hash, diagnostics

  alt diagnostics.unresolved_variables non-empty
    Agent->>Agent: abort or fill defaults
  end

  Note over Agent: 4. Use rendered prompt with LLM

  Agent->>LLM: chat.completions(rendered_system, rendered_user)
  LLM-->>Agent: response

  Note over Agent,AIEval: 5. (Optional) Forward rendered prompt + output to evaluation

  Agent->>AIEval: store {rendered_hash, version_id, output}
  AIEval-->>Agent: eval result (async)

  Note over Agent: 6. Improvement loop — bump version when prompt evolves

  Agent->>PromptOps: POST /versions {version: '1.1.0', body, changelog}
  Agent->>PromptOps: POST /versions/{newVid}/promote
